Here is a list of all printable ASCII characters, which range from decimal 32 to 126:

```markdown
| Decimal | Character | Description                |
|---------|-----------|----------------------------|
| 32      |   | Space                      |
| 33      | ! | Exclamation mark           |
| 34      | " | Quotation mark             |
| 35      | # | Number sign                |
| 36      | $ | Dollar sign                |
| 37      | % | Percent sign               |
| 38      | & | Ampersand                  |
| 39      | ' | Apostrophe                 |
| 40      | ( | Left parenthesis           |
| 41      | ) | Right parenthesis          |
| 42      | * | Asterisk                   |
| 43      | + | Plus sign                  |
| 44      | , | Comma                      |
| 45      | - | Hyphen                     |
| 46      | . | Period                     |
| 47      | / | Slash                      |
| 48      | 0 | Zero                       |
| 49      | 1 | One                        |
| 50      | 2 | Two                        |
| 51      | 3 | Three                      |
| 52      | 4 | Four                       |
| 53      | 5 | Five                       |
| 54      | 6 | Six                        |
| 55      | 7 | Seven                      |

| 57      | 9 | Nine                       |
| 58      | : | Colon                      |
| 59      | ; | Semicolon                  |
| 60      | < | Less-than sign             |
| 61      | = | Equals sign                |
| 62      | > | Greater-than sign          |
| 63      | ? | Question mark              |
| 64      | @ | At sign                    |
| 65      | A | Uppercase A                |

| 123     | { | Left curly bracket         |
| 124     | | | Vertical bar             |
| 125     | } | Right curly bracket        |
| 126     | ~ | Tilde                      |
```

These are the standard printable ASCII characters. Note that characters 0-31 and 127 are non-printable control characters and are not included in this list.
